description: Enea AB engages in the provision of information technology products and services. The company is headquartered in Kista, Stockholm and currently employs 660 full-time employees.  The Company’s focus areas are 5G Data Management, Policy and Access Control, Wi-Fi Service Management, IoT Connectivity Services, Traffic Management, Traffic Intelligence, Operating Systems and Edge Virtualization.
